      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’ve hit a wall and there’s just nothing left. all the years of work, the labs, the funding... it’s all just gone. i don’t even know who i am without this research. i’m just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me. i just want everything to stop. i just want peace.",
